---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Safety & Conduct">
<div class="conduct-page">

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="cond-hero">
    <div class="cond-tag">Safety & Conduct</div>
    <h1 class="cond-h1">The only rule: don't be <em>weird.</em></h1>
    <p class="cond-sub">Seriously, that's about it. Be cool to people. If someone's having a bad time because of you, we'll have a conversation. If it keeps happening, you're out. That's the whole policy.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- SAFETY BY DESIGN -->
  <section class="cond-section">
    <h2 class="cond-h2">🛡️ How the site keeps things safe</h2>
    <p class="cond-p">We built some stuff into the platform so people can feel comfortable showing up:</p>
    <div class="cond-features">
      <div class="cond-feature">
        <strong>Locations are hidden</strong>
        <p>You don't see where an event is until you RSVP. No one's randomly browsing addresses.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cond-feature">
        <strong>Every event has a host</strong>
        <p>There's always someone accountable. If something feels off, you know who to talk to.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cond-feature">
        <strong>Events are moderated</strong>
        <p>Anyone can suggest an event, but it gets reviewed before going live.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cond-feature">
        <strong>Small groups</strong>
        <p>6–12 people. Small enough that hosts can actually pay attention to the vibe.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WOMEN'S SAFETY -->
  <section class="cond-section">
    <h2 class="cond-h2">For women especially</h2>
    <p class="cond-p">We know showing up to a stranger meetup can feel different if you're a woman. We want you to know we've thought about that:</p>
    <div class="cond-callout women">
      <div class="cond-callout-items">
        <div class="cond-callout-item">
          <span class="cond-check">✓</span>
          <div>
            <strong>This isn't a dating app</strong>
            <p>People are here to meet friends. If something happens naturally, cool — but don't come here to hit on people. If someone's not interested, take the hint.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="cond-callout-item">
          <span class="cond-check">✓</span>
          <div>
            <strong>Report anything — even if you're not sure</strong>
            <p>You don't need to prove it was "bad enough." If someone made you uncomfortable, that's enough. We'd rather hear about a false alarm than miss something real.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="cond-callout-item">
          <span class="cond-check">✓</span>
          <div>
            <strong>We believe you</strong>
            <p>No devil's advocate. No "are you sure?" If you felt unsafe, that person is gone.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="cond-callout-item">
          <span class="cond-check">✓</span>
          <div>
            <strong>Your info stays private</strong>
            <p>Other members only see your first name and neighborhood. Email, phone, last name — never shared.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="cond-callout-item">
          <span class="cond-check">✓</span>
          <div>
            <strong>Bring a friend</strong>
            <p>First time and want a +1? Go for it. Just RSVP for both.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="cond-callout-item">
          <span class="cond-check">✓</span>
          <div>
            <strong>Public places only</strong>
            <p>Restaurants, parks, bowling alleys, coffee shops. No private residences.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- THE LINE -->
  <section class="cond-section">
    <h2 class="cond-h2">Where's the line?</h2>
    <p class="cond-p">We're pretty relaxed. But if someone tells us you made them uncomfortable, we're going to listen to them. Here's the stuff that'll get you removed immediately — no conversation, no second chance:</p>
    <div class="cond-callout red">
      <div class="cond-list">
        <div class="cond-list-item red"><span>✕</span> Sexual harassment or unwanted advances</div>
        <div class="cond-list-item red"><span>✕</span> Threatening or intimidating someone</div>
        <div class="cond-list-item red"><span>✕</span> Following someone after an event</div>
        <div class="cond-list-item red"><span>✕</span> Sharing someone's location or private info</div>
        <div class="cond-list-item red"><span>✕</span> Making someone feel unsafe — full stop</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="cond-p" style="margin-top:16px;">Everything else? We'll talk to you first. Showing up too drunk, being rude, trying to sell people stuff — you'll hear from Seth before anything else happens. Most people just need a heads up and it's fine.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- REPORTING -->
  <section class="cond-section">
    <h2 class="cond-h2">📢 If something happens</h2>
    <p class="cond-p">Tell the event host, message Seth on Discord, or send an email. Whatever's easiest. Your name stays between us — we're not going to make it a group discussion. We'll handle it and let you know what we did.</p>
    <div class="cond-report-btns">
      <a href="https://discord.gg/S8SFNkdSgK" class="cond-btn discord" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Message Seth on Discord</a>
      <a href="mailto:stharpe98@gmail.com" class="cond-btn email">Email Seth directly</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- GRACE -->
  <section class="cond-section">
    <div class="cond-callout blue">
      <h3>💬 One more thing</h3>
      <p>Being awkward at your first event? Normal. Saying something dumb? Happens. Running late because I-25 is a parking lot? Every time.</p>
      <p>This page isn't about being perfect. It's about making sure everyone can relax and have fun. If you read this far, you're probably exactly the kind of person we want around.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

</div>

<style is:inline>
  .conduct-page { max-width: 660px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px 48px; }

  .cond-hero { padding: 36px 0 32px; }
  .cond-tag {
    display: inline-block; font-size: 10px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .08em;
    color: #7C3AED; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 14px;
    padding: 5px 12px; background: rgba(124,58,237,0.06); border-radius: 50px;
    font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
  }
  .cond-h1 {
    font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; font-size: clamp(26px, 4vw, 34px);
    color: #111827; line-height: 1.15; margin-bottom: 14px; font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }
  .cond-h1 em { font-style: normal; color: #7C3AED; }
  .cond-sub { font-size: 14px; color: #6B7280; line-height: 1.7; max-width: 520px; }

  .cond-section { margin-bottom: 36px; }
  .cond-h2 {
    font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 800;
    color: #111827; margin-bottom: 10px; letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .cond-p { font-size: 13px; color: #6B7280; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px; }

  .cond-features { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 10px; }
  .cond-feature {
    padding: 14px 16px; border-radius: 12px;
    background: #F8F9FB; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;
  }
  .cond-feature strong { display: block; font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: #111827; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .cond-feature p { font-size: 11px; color: #6B7280; line-height: 1.5; }

  .cond-callout { border-radius: 16px; padding: 20px 24px; }
  .cond-callout.women {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(124,58,237,0.03), rgba(219,39,119,0.03));
    border: 1px solid rgba(124,58,237,0.12);
  }
  .cond-callout.red { background: rgba(248,113,113,0.04); border: 1px solid rgba(248,113,113,0.15); }
  .cond-callout.blue { background: rgba(96,165,250,0.04); border: 1px solid rgba(96,165,250,0.15); padding: 24px; }
  .cond-callout.blue h3 { font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; font-size: 15px; color: #111827; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .cond-callout.blue p { font-size: 13px; color: #6B7280; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .cond-callout.blue p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

  .cond-callout-items { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; }
  .cond-callout-item { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px; }
  .cond-check {
    width: 22px; height: 22px; flex-shrink: 0; border-radius: 6px;
    background: rgba(124,58,237,0.08); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    color: #7C3AED; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; margin-top: 1px;
  }
  .cond-callout-item strong { display: block; font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; color: #111827; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 2px; }
  .cond-callout-item p { font-size: 12px; color: #6B7280; line-height: 1.6; }

  .cond-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
  .cond-list-item { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 10px; font-size: 13px; color: #6B7280; line-height: 1.5; }
  .cond-list-item span { flex-shrink: 0; font-weight: 700; margin-top: 1px; }
  .cond-list-item.red span { color: #f87171; }

  .cond-report-btns { display: flex; gap: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .cond-btn {
    display: inline-block; padding: 11px 22px; border-radius: 50px;
    font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: none; transition: all .2s;
  }
  .cond-btn.discord { background: #5865F2; color: #fff; }
  .cond-btn.discord:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(88,101,242,0.3); }
  .cond-btn.email { background: #F8F9FB; color: #6B7280; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB; }
  .cond-btn.email:hover { border-color: #D1D5DB; color: #111827; }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .cond-features { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
</Base>
